{"tid":2022852,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【病毒中轉港】教你點用美國司法系統捅林鄭一刀","createTime":"2020-05-18T14:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T17:12:21.000Z","uid":70786,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"eedb67c0ad677c136d725ef5eb1ad00a246dbaba","tid":2022852,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"想開去突發但衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再開過<br />\n首先希望大家去Twitter撥下火先<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/julian_direct/status/1262279103291383809?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjulian_direct%2Fstatus%2F1262279103291383809%3Fs%3D20&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=8e758a57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjulian_direct%2Fstatus%2F1262279103291383809%3Fs%3D20&h=6e40625c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/julian_direct/status/1262279103291383809?s=20</a><br />\n但係做Twitter都唔夠，香港人仲可以同林鄭玩個更好玩嘅遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴住阿婆底褲仲咁撚臭串？香港人攬炒就係要林鄭同行會仆街死！<br />\n<br />\n呢一年嚟發生嘅事，特別係今日立法會發生嘅事係咪令你覺得好嬲？<br />\n嬲係冇用嘅，香港人要學識將憤怒化成動力，繼續做自己能力而內可以做嘅事<br />\n我係上年雙十一爆買黃店嘅其中一個發起人<br />\n依家見到黃色經濟圈發到咁大真係完全估唔到，亦都好欣慰<br />\n但係除咗本地街頭戰線外，都想大家放多D時間打國際戰線<br />\n<br />\n唔使自己花費一分一毫就可以告鳩中港共，擺林鄭上檯，等人地幫你查港共有冇份幫手播毒，贏咗仲隨時有錢分，係咪好吸引好想知點做？<br />\n就係用香港政府最驚又非法嘅包攬訴訟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事先講明，包攬訴訟喺美國係合法嘅<br />\n美國律師一聞到有case就會主動聯絡受害人，幫手打贏官司再瓜分賠償<br />\n佢地為咗要贏真係會仆心仆命，唔使擔心佢地會揸流灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n具體做法就係要搵一班有美國籍嘅巴絲打<br />\n（之前美國手足寄豬嘴返香港嘅團隊Free HK USA應該每個州都有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n聯絡已經對中國播毒展開訴訟嘅律師行<br />\n（詳細資料去Google class aciton lawsuit+China+Coronavirus/Covid-19應該就會搵到邊d州份有份告支那，只要跟據自己州份再去聯絡相關律師行就可以) <br />\n<br />\n參與訴訟理由自己諗啦，例如出入口管制同隔離搞到有經濟上損失<br />\n或者學業受阻，都係入稟嘅理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功join完之後就要幫手搜集上庭可以用嘅子彈<br />\n<br />\n其中有兩個Post好值得大家追下，同幫手整理時序加核對，為真相搵出更多拼圖！<br />\n<blockquote>白宮首席經濟顧問: 中國遣送數千萬國民坐飛機到全球各地散播病毒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2021485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2021485</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭係導致全球病毒大爆發幫兇 ..... Twitter 煲大佢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fuLnLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fuLnLS</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最值得留意癲狗日報記者於4月28日當面問林鄭有冇份促成全球爆發後所撰寫嘅報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/glocalizedlifestyle/posts/156893309191249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fglocalizedlifestyle%2Fposts%2F156893309191249&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=093e600d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/glocalizedlifestyle/posts/156893309191249</a><br />\n<br />\n睇返當中1月入境人數報告(1月23日前入境資料被官方刪除，原因不明<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fmessage_from_us%2Fstat2.html&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=eb2250b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat2.html</a>奶共狗曾國衛識唔識咩叫欲蓋彌彰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家記得幫手癲狗日報留底）<br />\n1月一直都有大量支那人由香港機場離境，當中咩人去邊個國家，機管局一定有資料<br />\n唔好諗住又刪資料，因為外國一樣有出入境紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭於1月28日先公布1月30日局部封關措施，比起首宗確診足足遲咗多過一個星期！<br />\n醫護係點罷工要求林鄭封關而林鄭一直拒絕，香港人一定記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2003年SARS時任社會福利署署長林鄭唔可能唔知道呼吸系統冠狀病毒嘅嚴重性，12月已經開始傳武漢出事，林鄭等到1月28日先宣佈1月30日封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他林鄭抗疫施政失誤包括但不限於：<br />\n搵梁卓偉出嚟話戴口罩講唔到野<br />\n見到公務員戴咗口罩都要佢除翻落嚟<br />\n支那爆唔封關，韓國爆即封關<br />\n<br />\n歡迎咁多位巴絲打幫手補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b24025490c9ad18e3ef8541b1e2e13c683cf44a","tid":2022852,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港於 1 月 21 日出現首宗輸入的新型冠狀病毒確診個案，患者為武漢人，1 月在 21 日搭高鐵來港，在高鐵西九龍站被發現發燒，即時送院隔離。而同行家人沒有病徵，於 1 月 22 日已轉飛菲律賓馬尼拉。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>首5宗香港本地確診個案均由武漢經高鐵傳入</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>根據武漢國際機場資料顯示，由去年12月30日，國際航班人流最多的目的地為香港。至而日本首名確診患者，為中國人，正是由武漢經香港轉機到日本。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f99b201ed466776520d48e29e4f616661e00611c","tid":2022852,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5827d3b494449d510d0fab021460236aa86a2f59","tid":2022852,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9ed03511d31f713c8f9c4f2366f313394f10ef9d","tid":2022852,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d43a902147ce85068cdca273f832f8799401ac0","tid":2022852,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府主動指示醫管局秋後算賬罷工醫護<br />\n<br />\n報告主動向中央匯報，指政府已要求醫管局嚴肅處理組織罷工的員工，「不應容許害群之馬留在醫院工作」，口徑與中聯辦喉舌建制輿論如出一轍。<br />\n首先，醫院管理局並唔係一個政府部門，醫生護士亦唔係公務員，亦無需所謂政治中立，即係報告顯示政府用緊政治力量打壓政見不同人士<br />\n再者，基本法寫明香港人有罷工權利。報告中政府指示醫管局秋後算賬無疑係違反基本法嘅鐵證</blockquote>"},{"pid":"39db89af724256fe43cbc22a52662f9e9e18ebfe","tid":2022852,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98edc0f28d163509fce21d388c9dce8c90f9991","tid":2022852,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc68b9921a96b8f79ee1ec36db2fdd57fecad33","tid":2022852,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ac440247c0ad7c04bb806e6e7ae2840a163059","tid":2022852,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc1a6f02bcf8feb7b508282e8749e43ccf0d1a4","tid":2022852,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:47:26.000Z","msg":"香港人唔係憎林鄭憎到仆街咩<br />\n幫下手推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b62e8d435ebbbb635afaaa85a811239000bdc3","tid":2022852,"uid":350019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eedb67c0ad677c136d725ef5eb1ad00a246dbaba","tid":2022852,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"想開去突發但衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再開過<br />\n首先希望大家去Twitter撥下火先<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/julian_direct/status/1262279103291383809?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjulian_direct%2Fstatus%2F1262279103291383809%3Fs%3D20&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=8e758a57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjulian_direct%2Fstatus%2F1262279103291383809%3Fs%3D20&h=6e40625c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/julian_direct/status/1262279103291383809?s=20</a><br />\n但係做Twitter都唔夠，香港人仲可以同林鄭玩個更好玩嘅遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴住阿婆底褲仲咁撚臭串？香港人攬炒就係要林鄭同行會仆街死！<br />\n<br />\n呢一年嚟發生嘅事，特別係今日立法會發生嘅事係咪令你覺得好嬲？<br />\n嬲係冇用嘅，香港人要學識將憤怒化成動力，繼續做自己能力而內可以做嘅事<br />\n我係上年雙十一爆買黃店嘅其中一個發起人<br />\n依家見到黃色經濟圈發到咁大真係完全估唔到，亦都好欣慰<br />\n但係除咗本地街頭戰線外，都想大家放多D時間打國際戰線<br />\n<br />\n唔使自己花費一分一毫就可以告鳩中港共，擺林鄭上檯，等人地幫你查港共有冇份幫手播毒，贏咗仲隨時有錢分，係咪好吸引好想知點做？<br />\n就係用香港政府最驚又非法嘅包攬訴訟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事先講明，包攬訴訟喺美國係合法嘅<br />\n美國律師一聞到有case就會主動聯絡受害人，幫手打贏官司再瓜分賠償<br />\n佢地為咗要贏真係會仆心仆命，唔使擔心佢地會揸流灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n具體做法就係要搵一班有美國籍嘅巴絲打<br />\n（之前美國手足寄豬嘴返香港嘅團隊Free HK USA應該每個州都有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n聯絡已經對中國播毒展開訴訟嘅律師行<br />\n（詳細資料去Google class aciton lawsuit+China+Coronavirus/Covid-19應該就會搵到邊d州份有份告支那，只要跟據自己州份再去聯絡相關律師行就可以) <br />\n<br />\n參與訴訟理由自己諗啦，例如出入口管制同隔離搞到有經濟上損失<br />\n或者學業受阻，都係入稟嘅理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功join完之後就要幫手搜集上庭可以用嘅子彈<br />\n<br />\n其中有兩個Post好值得大家追下，同幫手整理時序加核對，為真相搵出更多拼圖！<br />\n<blockquote>白宮首席經濟顧問: 中國遣送數千萬國民坐飛機到全球各地散播病毒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2021485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2021485</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭係導致全球病毒大爆發幫兇 ..... Twitter 煲大佢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fuLnLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fuLnLS</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最值得留意癲狗日報記者於4月28日當面問林鄭有冇份促成全球爆發後所撰寫嘅報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/glocalizedlifestyle/posts/156893309191249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fglocalizedlifestyle%2Fposts%2F156893309191249&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=093e600d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/glocalizedlifestyle/posts/156893309191249</a><br />\n<br />\n睇返當中1月入境人數報告(1月23日前入境資料被官方刪除，原因不明<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fmessage_from_us%2Fstat2.html&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=eb2250b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat2.html</a>奶共狗曾國衛識唔識咩叫欲蓋彌彰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家記得幫手癲狗日報留底）<br />\n1月一直都有大量支那人由香港機場離境，當中咩人去邊個國家，機管局一定有資料<br />\n唔好諗住又刪資料，因為外國一樣有出入境紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭於1月28日先公布1月30日局部封關措施，比起首宗確診足足遲咗多過一個星期！<br />\n醫護係點罷工要求林鄭封關而林鄭一直拒絕，香港人一定記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2003年SARS時任社會福利署署長林鄭唔可能唔知道呼吸系統冠狀病毒嘅嚴重性，12月已經開始傳武漢出事，林鄭等到1月28日先宣佈1月30日封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他林鄭抗疫施政失誤包括但不限於：<br />\n搵梁卓偉出嚟話戴口罩講唔到野<br />\n見到公務員戴咗口罩都要佢除翻落嚟<br />\n支那爆唔封關，韓國爆即封關<br />\n<br />\n歡迎咁多位巴絲打幫手補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"713c943e9cf937074416bff7130bf326004edf5d","tid":2022852,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b657294cca3637b1efe7c3b3b1e4c78a5042cd77","tid":2022852,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"重要，推"},{"pid":"89346a681ee5f791fefb25734bd8216055591490","tid":2022852,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:50:25.000Z","msg":"人人都可以係星星之火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ec7a47558f225200713f894774b3cdffe84795","tid":2022852,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"23f908cedcab8ddd6563010788c085d85c08c7bf","tid":2022852,"uid":164761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:52:07.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e6dde6580a7cde6bc5f88961e6c71ed42bd4ce","tid":2022852,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94220d639b71c011fbae6f2593f1b0f40205153","tid":2022852,"uid":34154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇返當中1月入境人數報告(1月23日前入境資料被官方刪除，原因不明<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat2.html奶共狗曾國衛識唔識咩叫欲蓋彌彰\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fmessage_from_us%2Fstat2.html%E5%A5%B6%E5%85%B1%E7%8B%97%E6%9B%BE%E5%9C%8B%E8%A1%9B%E8%AD%98%E5%94%94%E8%AD%98%E5%92%A9%E5%8F%AB%E6%AC%B2%E8%93%8B%E5%BD%8C%E5%BD%B0&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=2508b01b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat2.html奶共狗曾國衛識唔識咩叫欲蓋彌彰</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家記得幫手癲狗日報留底）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇返Wayback Machine入面「出入境人數統計」呢個網頁個紀錄, web crawler keep低咗最舊嘅version 係2月11日 (代表個crawler 2月11日第一次揾到同save低呢個網頁, 唔代表個網頁幾時create出嚟), 會唔會係呢啲statistics係1月尾先開始公開?<br />\n不過我想講嘅係，如果你發現正苦網頁某啲資料消失咗，可以上去Wayback Machine到睇下d web crawler有冇留到底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/*/https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat_menu.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F%2A%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fmessage_from_us%2Fstat_me