.html&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=eb2250b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat2.html</a>奶共狗曾國衛識唔識咩叫欲蓋彌彰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家記得幫手癲狗日報留底）<br />\n1月一直都有大量支那人由香港機場離境，當中咩人去邊個國家，機管局一定有資料<br />\n唔好諗住又刪資料，因為外國一樣有出入境紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭於1月28日先公布1月30日局部封關措施，比起首宗確診足足遲咗多過一個星期！<br />\n醫護係點罷工要求林鄭封關而林鄭一直拒絕，香港人一定記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2003年SARS時任社會福利署署長林鄭唔可能唔知道呼吸系統冠狀病毒嘅嚴重性，12月已經開始傳武漢出事，林鄭等到1月28日先宣佈1月30日封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他林鄭抗疫施政失誤包括但不限於：<br />\n搵梁卓偉出嚟話戴口罩講唔到野<br />\n見到公務員戴咗口罩都要佢除翻落嚟<br />\n支那爆唔封關，韓國爆即封關<br />\n<br />\n歡迎咁多位巴絲打幫手補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:51:30.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"68b4263e819191aec98a853cfc622e286d6d4f08","tid":2022852,"uid":252325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:52:15.000Z","msg":"冇美藉都幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359395399b2839587fcc2e442df6f8bc22d42b95","tid":2022852,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:54:29.000Z","msg":"支持 但推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6770db35ded3e029b33873eed7d4f8637e3d27df","tid":2022852,"uid":149092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b724570f4b18ec00f45ae98cdf0949f1daafd8cb","tid":2022852,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff15efe2991bca142b84f73ccbd4ea404fa2e58","tid":2022852,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/ass